## Output format

Once the experiment finishes, it prints a summary block starting with `---`. Example:

```
---
{{ metric_name }}:{{ " " * (18 - metric_name|length) }}1234.56
{%- for c in constraints %}
{{ c.name }}:{{ " " * (18 - c.name|length) }}0.00
{%- endfor %}
```

You can extract the key metric from the log file:

```
grep "^{{ metric_name }}:" run.log
```

